the Cleric epic is probably thee most powerful item in the game. without that little cliky rez it would take a guild of 40 or so members on a wipe and 1 cleric making camp, about an hour, if not an hour and a half to get back up to raid strength, rezzing a tank or two, rezzing another cleric, then a chanter, bard...whatnot, it would take a good amount of time to rez everyone and to get them back to raid status.<br>
