with a cleric  epic, it takes that same raid abuot 15-20 min to get running again. click on every corpse and just keep clicking till everyone is standing, no cast it 5 times, and med for 5 min to get mana for another rez. much less buff mana (granted MGB Aego does cut down this as well).<br>
