<br>
Remember it is not anyones RIGHT to get an epic it is a symbol of hard work and dedication.  The list implies the people at the top of the list have more RIGHT to an epic than the people at the bottom and I think that is in no way true.  Personally I think that if they want the list to last they need to put level 60s at the front of the list then 59s then 58s and throw out anyone lower till they get their levels.  The epic is a symbol of prestige especially with the clerics and I really don't think a level 53 cleric has earned that kind of honor. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=97672">
